high_descs: Move to the stove on the other side of the island.
Pick up the cup inside the microwave above the stove before closing the door.
Turn around to the sink behind you.
Place the cup inside the sink.
Pick up the fork from inside the sink.
Put the fork inside the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the cup from the microwave in the sink with a fork in it.

high_descs: turn right, walk to the  wall, turn left and head into the kitchen. Turn left in the kitchen and stop at the stove to your right.
open the microwave above the stove and take out the green cup.
turn to your left and go to the sink behind you.
put the green cup in the sink.
grab the fork out of the sink.
put the fork in the green cup that is in the sink
Walk around the kitchen island to the stove
Open the microwave above the stove and remove the green cup
Turn around and go to the kitchen sink
Put the cup into the sink
Pick up the fork from the sink
Put the fork into the green cup
anns.task_desc: Put the fork into the green cup in the sink

high_descs: Walk around the counter, walk in front of the stove.
Take the green cup out of the microwave above the stove.
Turn around, go to the sink.
Put the green cup in the sink.
Pick up the fork next to the tomato.
Put the fork in the green cup.
anns.task_desc: Put the cup with the fork in it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the right of the island.  Go to the stove.
Open the microwave.  Grab the green cup that is to the left of the white one. Shut the microwave door.
With the green cup in hand turn all the way around to go to the sink.
Place the cup in the sink to the left of the fork.
Pick up the fork that is in the sink and to the left of the tomato.
Place the fork in the cup that is in the sink.
